      • ConfigureAgentWindow

        public ConfigureAgentWindow(javax.swing.JFrame parent,
                            boolean modal)
        Constructor that is called from the Simulator main to create the configure window.
        Parameters:
        parent - JFrame of the parent that is going to create this dialog.
        modal - Boolean that says to the dialog if the dialog created is modal or not. True: Is modal so you can't accede to the contain that is below before you close the dialog. False: It isn't modal so you can accede to the contain is below the dialog.
